Neighborhood Adventures." Let's explore Sesame Street! You unlocked a new sticker!
Wonderful, wonderful! (door squeaks) (paper shuffles) - [Count Dracula] Greetings!
It is I the Count! And I am writing one very
special letter to you! (upbeat music) - Great catching! Wow. Nice catching! (peppy music) - What kind of bird am I?
Well, I'm Big Bird, of course. - Well, Elmo has a stuffie,
but he's not a bear. He's a baby! - Are you into movies? Me, actually a big film buff you know. - [Character] Some of my magical beasties living in my garden have gotten lost! And my magical plants and
flowers are missing too! You can find the Beasties. I'm sure the plants will grow back. (pleasant music) - Beastie? Yes, I believe I saw one, over in that direction
in which I am pointing. (pleasant music continues)
